snippet.title: SLAY-BELLS   -   Teaser
snippet.description:
This is a short little teaser video to show what I've been working on for my 3D Platformer "Slay-Bells" ^^

I hope you all enjoy this short little video showcasing a few (W.I.P) sections of the game!
